OOC: Ignroe my last post except the OOC. Dewboy, care to tell me how thirst 
broke free when a claw was imbedded in his back?

IC:

The kick met its mark and sent Void spinning in the air before hitting the 
ground. He then rose to his feet and staggered as he held the side of his 
face that was kicked, a neat imprint being present. Void scowled and then 
drew his blaster once again and fired several more blasts at Thirst as his 
cloak then opened and one of those flying creatures once again flew out and 
then exploded a few inches from Thirst, the explosion also sending Void 
sprawling to the ground given their close proximity.

--part1_b0.215e645e.298eb333_boundary
